      "spell_level": "alchemist 2, cleric/oracle 2, druid 2, inquisitor 2, paladin 2, ranger 1, sorcerer/wizard 2, summoner/unchained summoner 2, bloodrager 2, shaman 2, occultist 2, psychic 2, spiritualist 2",
